<head>
    <title>Test your memory</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/brain.ico">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/test.css">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<div class="container info">
    <h1>Memory Test</h1>
</div>
<div id="words" class="container">
    <p>There are twelve words you need to remember. Please concentrate for a few seconds
    on each word and click <b>Next</b> to check how many you managed to remember.</p>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="column">
            <p>Tiger</p>
            <p>Violet</p>
            <p>Sun</p>
            <p>Hello</p>
            <p>Forest</p>
            <p>Teapot</p>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
            <img src="/images/test-img-recall.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="column">
            <p>Magic</p>
            <p>Holiday</p>
            <p>Game</p>
            <p>Success</p>
            <p>Blossom</p>
            <p>Orange</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn-game" onclick="displayForm()">Next</a>
</div>
<div id="form" class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="column">
            <input id="tiger" name="tiger" type="text">
            <input id="violet" name="violet" type="text">
            <input id="sun" name="sun" type="text">
            <input id="hello" name="hello" type="text">
            <input id="forest" name="forest" type="text">
            <input id="teapot" name="teapot" type="text">
        </div>
        <div class="column">
            <img src="/images/test-img-recall.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="column">
            <input id="magic" name="magic" type="text">
            <input id="holiday" name="holiday" type="text">
            <input id="game" name="game" type="text">
            <input id="success" name="success" type="text">
            <input id="blossom" name="blossom" type="text">
            <input id="orange" name="orange" type="text">
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn-game" onclick="checkForm()">Check</a>
</div>
<div id="result" class="container">
    <h2>Thank you for completing the test!</h2>
    <img src="/images/test-img-research.png" alt="">
</div>
<div id="start" class="container">
    <p>The cognitive psychologist George A. Miller of Harvard University's Department of Psychology
         has written an article which states that the number of objects an average human can hold in short-term memory is 7 Â± 2.
        You can find out more about his research
        <a href="http://www2.psych.utoronto.ca/users/peterson/psy430s2001/Miller%20GA%20Magical%20Seven%20Psych%20Review%201955.pdf"><b>here</b>!</a></p>
    <p>For now, you can compare your score to this "magical number 7" and try out our games to improve your
    cognitive skills!</p>
    <a href="/" class="btn btn-game">Start</a>
</div>

<script src='/js/test.js'></script>

